name: Fauna Flowers 10 - Guará Flower
description:
This shy flower lives in  Cerrado, one of the largest biomes in South America. If you are patient and smart, you can find it in this huge savannah. You don't need to be afraid, cause it's friendly and adorable. If you cross its path, lucky you!

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
